---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import PlaceholderBackground from "../../assets/background/blocks-grid.avif";
---

<div class="w-full max-w-[100dvw] relative h-auto py-20">
  <div
    class="w-full max-w-[100dvw] z-[1] relative mx-auto md:max-w-[1200px] flex flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4"
  >
  <p class="absolute -top-12 tracking-tighter bottom-auto left-6 right-auto text-6xl font-black text-[var(--ghost-a1)]">About Don</p>
    <div
      class="w-2/3 flex flex-col gap-6 items-start justify-start p-10 border-[4px] border-[var(--ghost-a1)] bg-[var(--lime-a1)] backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl shadow-2xl"
    >
      <p>
        Talented and driven Visual Communicator with a proven record of
        delivering customized innovative design solutions, leading by example,
        growing accounts, fostering successful teams, and strengthening client
        relationships to deliver on aggressive goals in dead-line sensitive
        competitive industries.
      </p><p>
        Strict attention to detail and strong organizational skills - supporting
        demanding customers and partnering with sales, clients, and production
        to produce a wide-range of in-store, digital, and printcommunications -
        from conception to final file distribution, ensuring that all work meets
        brand standards and delivered within agreed timelines.
      </p><p>
        Dynamic team player with a passion for contributing to best-in-class
        marketing, sales, and service environments. Exceptional collaborative
        and interpersonal skills, can communicate effectively with all levels of
        the organization, managing multiple projects and competing priorities.
      </p><p>
        Imaginative Graphic Designer working with creative teams to design
        content for marketing, advertisements, promotions, branding, products,
        and services applied across a wide range of multimedia applications. I
        love putting the finishing touches on the art that really matters in the
        business world, establishing and maintaining your brand.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="w-1/3"></div>
  </div>

  <Image
    src={PlaceholderBackground}
    alt="test"
    loading="eager"
    decoding="async"
    class="absolute left-0 right-0 top-0 bottom-0 object-cover object-center m-0 w-full h-full -z-[1] touch-none select-none brightness-0 pointer-events-none"
  />
</div>
